The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for license plate detection and recognition, which are typical topics in the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of deep neural networks (DNNs) also suggests that the paper could be relevant to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The problem of false positives and bounding box refinement also involves some aspects of computer security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper deals with image processing and pattern recognition, which are relevant to the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
